{"tid":1738476,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"催淚彈射入屋 焚毀民宅","createTime":"2019-11-19T09:09:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T10:54:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d7a724545b4c056e5c06e25a54cbd6ae9aae5b3b","tid":1738476,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:09:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191119/PZGUUV4FCIJTQIWFQFFPT2IS2M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191119%2FPZGUUV4FCIJTQIWFQFFPT2IS2M%2F&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4Mqv%2BqeKGcMvuhkm4gAZs5aLs%3D&h=36db0b96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191119%2FPZGUUV4FCIJTQIWFQFFPT2IS2M%2F&h=d1ea1a37\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191119/PZGUUV4FCIJTQIWFQFFPT2IS2M/</a><br />\n<br />\n催淚彈射入屋 焚毀民宅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方的催淚彈放題再度誤中副車。佐敦柯士甸路一個住宅單位，昨早因防暴警亂射催淚彈驅散人群期間，其中兩發破窗射入房間，導致室內起火，近半間屋焚漽，幸當時無人身處房內，否則恐釀成傷亡，女戶主正與律師商討，計劃向警方提出民事索償。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：攀山爬草叢 狂衝馬路脫困<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/jWzODK6ZBVW_ys4jabl3I2F7E5o=/802x612/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/6BQQZK6JWBIFAWONOLHZPK7QTQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FjWzODK6ZBVW_ys4jabl3I2F7E5o%3D%2F802x612%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F6BQQZK6JWBIFAWONOLHZPK7QTQ.gif&h=d7f88855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n催淚彈破窗射入戶主女兒房間，整間房幾乎焚。黎敬中攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/zr24JjdPjno_2g-n5gYmGgq0OOQ=/802x793/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/OQCB37II5DDGYICPYWHCPNUVOI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fzr24JjdPjno_2g-n5gYmGgq0OOQ%3D%2F802x793%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FOQCB37II5DDGYICPYWHCPNUVOI.gif&h=85c6480d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戶主搜尋下在房內發現兩個催淚彈彈頭。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/zN6ZwkzpJiZRkOUf-Bhv_6HVPXE=/802x506/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/I22MQCSQSNUNRF7MMTTN6VLDJA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FzN6ZwkzpJiZRkOUf-Bhv_6HVPXE%3D%2F802x506%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FI22MQCSQSNUNRF7MMTTN6VLDJA.gif&h=f34e3c5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有柯士甸路客貨車遭催淚彈擊破尾門玻璃射入車內，車廂充斥刺鼻濃煙。何量鈞攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n戶主擬提民事索償<br />\n<br />\n居住豐樂大廈低層單位的女戶主郭小姐表示，警方昨早在佐敦柯士甸路一帶不斷施放催淚彈，至早上10時許家傭來電，「佢聽到兩下槍聲，到第三下時，屋企角落個窗口就被爆爛咗，跟住就開始出白煙同燒着附近啲書。」由於氣味極為刺鼻，患哮喘的女傭「眼淚標鼻涕流」，未待穿鞋便奪門而逃，身無分文找來同鄉借電話告知事件。<br />\n<br />\n郭小姐聞訊趕返家，獲鄰居告知家中失火，須由消防射水救熄。她入屋視察，赫見女兒房間牆身和天花熏黑，家中約有三分一地方被火勢波及，全屋地板有吋半高積水，伴隨而來濃烈的燒燶味，經搜尋在房內發現兩個催淚彈彈頭，相信警方誤射催淚彈入室內導致火災。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，幸事發一刻女傭在客廳打掃，「個女5分鐘前出咗門，冇人喺房，否則真係燒死人。」由於家中損漽嚴重，水浸有可能影響樓下單位，已保留兩個彈頭及被燒着的書本，聯絡律師安排公證行進行化驗，作為稍後向警方民事索償的證據。<br />\n<br />\n今次已非首次有催淚彈亂射入屋，上周四防暴警在沙田好運中心平台施射催淚彈驅散人群時，其中一枚催淚彈射穿玻璃直飛入屋，濃煙四散籠罩室內，夫婦帶同愛犬直奔落樓。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黎敬中"},{"pid":"c14f426e70310b559c267a16b52c4a3ff3ff5587","tid":1738476,"uid":287547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:11:05.000Z","msg":"[黃色經濟圈]你買我就代你捐一半<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1738473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1738473</a>"},{"pid":"fc4a8250dcd36c152e8091746e980d4567fb0c6f","tid":1738476,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:11:16.000Z","msg":"電光火石間"},{"pid":"8425ef0675cbf338aa9d16a1dff14e1e91c7bcd1","tid":1738476,"uid":163734,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:14:01.000Z","msg"